## рџ—‚ File Structure

```
backend-play/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ lib/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ mongodb.ts          в†ђ DB connection singleton
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ auth-options.ts     в†ђ NextAuth v5 config (Google + Credentials, JWT)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ game-content.ts     в†ђ ~120 static cards, shuffle utils
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ rate-limit.ts       в†ђ IP-based rate limiter
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ models/
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ User.ts             в†ђ Mongoose schema
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ middleware.ts            в†ђ Route protection (redirects to /login)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ types/
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ next-auth.d.ts      в†ђ Session type augmentation
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ app/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ api/auth/            в†ђ [...nextauth], signup, delete-account, forgot-password, reset-password
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ api/game/[mode]/     в†ђ Game content API
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ api/user/            в†ђ profile, subscription
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ login/page.tsx       в†ђ Minimal login (functional)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ signup/page.tsx      в†ђ Minimal signup (functional)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ components/
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ SessionProvider.tsx
в””в”Ђв”Ђ .env.local               в†ђ MONGODB_URI, NEXTAUTH_SECRET, Google OAuth, ALLOW_DEV_SUBSCRIPTION
```

## вљ™пёЏ Environment Variables Required

| Variable | Required | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `MONGODB_URI` | вњ… | MongoDB Atlas connection string |
| `NEXTAUTH_SECRET` | вњ… | JWT signing secret |
| `NEXTAUTH_URL` | вњ… | App base URL (`http://localhost:3000`) |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID` | For Google auth | Google OAuth |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET` | For Google auth | Google OAuth |
| `ALLOW_DEV_SUBSCRIPTION` | Dev only | Enables subscription toggle |
